    <div class="gem-c-title govuk-!-margin-top-8 govuk-!-margin-bottom-8">
    <span class="govuk-caption-xl gem-c-title__context">
      Press release
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Isotretinoin and suspected link with serious side effects: public and patients’ views sought
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">We are reviewing the risks and benefits of the acne medicine, isotretinoin. In particular whether some of the possible psychiatric and sexual side effects continue after treatment has been stopped.  </p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="metadata-logo-wrapper">
    <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds metadata-column">
        <div class="app-c-publisher-metadata" lang="en">
    <div class="app-c-published-dates " lang="en">
    Published 10 November 2020
</div>

      <div class="app-c-publisher-metadata__other">
        <dl data-module="track-click">
